Text: Undeliverable Re Energy Seminar in Japanmessage To Subject Re Energy Seminar in Japan Sent Wed Dec did not reach the following recipients on Wed Dec The recipient name is not recognized The MTSID of the original message is cUSa pISDAlISDANTYWDNTS MSEXCHIMSISDAISDANYISDANT CA Unknown Recipient MessageID From To Subject Re Energy Seminar in Japan Date Wed Dec MIMEVersion XMailer Internet Mail Service XMSEmbeddedReport ContentType textplain charsetiso I am hearing that it may be premature to do an ISDA energy conference in Tokyo because almost all the products being discussed so far are physical What do you think Mark Forwarded by Mark E HaedickeHOUECT on AM Jane NRON To Mark E CT cc Alan CT ECT Jonathan nron Morten E nron Mark AM CT Subject Re Energy Seminar in JapanDocument link Mark E Haedicke Hi Mark There will be a oneday WRMA conference here Morten Erik and Mark Tawney are involved in these arrangements and Mr Wani lawyer of local derivative fame will be talking at the conference in late Feb or early March Date will be fixed later this week likely to be March Jane Mark E CT To Jane nron Alan CT cc Subject Energy Seminar in Japan Jane ISDA is planning an energy seminar in Tokyo in midMay We have heard there may be an energy seminar in March or April in Tokyo Have you heard of the earlier seminar We are trying to decide whether it makes sense to go forward on the May seminar Could you look into this and talk to the traders Thanks for your help Regards Mark
